Dr. Dolittle;;34;;42;;PG-13;;After a fender bender, Dr. John Dolittle (Eddie Murphy) gets back his childhood ability to converse with animals. But the gift turns out to be a mixed blessing when the good doctor finds himself besieged by boozing monkeys, injured owls and depressed lions who need his special assistance. When Dolittle's strange behavior catches the attention of his wife, Lisa (Kristen Wilson), he winds up in a mental institution. Luckily, he has some animal friends to help him out of his hairy situation.;;Comedy;;Betty Thomas;;1998;;Eddie Murphy,Ossie Davis,Oliver Platt,Peter Boyle,Richard Schiff,Kristen Wilson,Jeffrey Tambor,Kyla Pratt,Raven-Symon√©,Steven Gilborn,Norm Macdonald,Albert Brooks,Chris Rock,Garry Shandling;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/dr_dolittle